00:02:17.167 --> 00:02:19.559
"Are they really out there?"

00:02:19.583 --> 00:02:22.018
(Laughter)

00:02:22.042 --> 00:02:25.684
All this goes double for LGBTQI
women's sexuality,

00:02:25.708 --> 00:02:28.917
which has been hated
and erased in specific ways.

00:02:30.333 --> 00:02:34.809
Ignorance about the female body
goes back centuries.

00:02:34.833 --> 00:02:37.518
It goes back to the beginning
of modern medicine.

00:02:37.542 --> 00:02:40.434
Cast your mind back to the 16th century,

00:02:40.458 --> 00:02:44.768
a time of scientific revolution in Europe.

00:02:44.792 --> 00:02:47.917
Men of ideas were challenging old dogmas.

00:02:48.750 --> 00:02:52.726
They were building telescopes
to gaze up at the stars.

00:02:52.750 --> 00:02:55.143
We were making progress ...

00:02:55.167 --> 00:02:56.684
sometimes.

00:02:56.708 --> 00:02:59.268
You see, the fathers of anatomy --

00:02:59.292 --> 00:03:03.518
and I say "fathers" because,
let's face it, they were all dudes --

00:03:03.542 --> 00:03:06.018
were poking about between women's legs

00:03:06.042 --> 00:03:08.917
and trying to classify what they saw.

00:03:09.833 --> 00:03:13.708
