00:03:39.333 --> 00:03:40.601
That's right.

00:03:40.625 --> 00:03:44.643
Something we think of today
as female genital mutilation

00:03:44.667 --> 00:03:48.833
was practiced in the West
as late as the 20th century.

00:03:49.958 --> 00:03:51.226
You have to wonder:

00:03:51.250 --> 00:03:54.434
if they were that confused
about women's bodies,

00:03:54.458 --> 00:03:56.958
why didn't they just ask women
for a little help?

00:03:58.667 --> 00:04:01.750
But you must be thinking,
"All that was history.

00:04:02.375 --> 00:04:04.684
