00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:46.208
They say, "I don't feel whole."

00:07:47.292 --> 00:07:51.417
They feel they've lost a connection
with their partners and themselves.

00:07:52.417 --> 00:07:55.226
So what is sex?

00:07:55.250 --> 00:07:58.184
We've traditionally defined the act of sex

00:07:58.208 --> 00:08:02.434
as a linear, goal-oriented process.

00:08:02.458 --> 00:08:05.143
It's something that starts with lust,

00:08:05.167 --> 00:08:08.101
