00:08:11.542 --> 00:08:14.583
Except many women
don't experience it this way.

00:08:18.042 --> 00:08:22.042
It's less linear for them
and more circular.

00:08:22.875 --> 00:08:26.268
This is a new model
of women's arousal and desire

00:08:26.292 --> 00:08:29.434
developed by Dr. Rosemary Basson.

00:08:29.458 --> 00:08:30.726
